welcome_message_body: Welcome to Lake Mohawk! Get ready to experience the charm of our beautiful city known for its stunning lake views and friendly community. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Lake Mohawk has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Municipal Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
